sections.Quotes:
{{Quote|I'm a Greyjoy. We've been Lords of the Iron Islands for hundreds of years. There's not a family in Westeros that can look down on us. Not even the Lannisters.|Theon Greyjoy|The Wolf and the Lion}}
{{Template:Dialogue a-b-a-b-a|Theon Greyjoy|Are you afraid?|Robb Stark|I must be.|Good.|Why is that good?|It means you're not stupid.|Theon to Robb before Robb's first battle.|The Pointy End}}
{{Quote|You gave me away! Your boy! Your last boy! You gave me away like I was some dog you didn't want anymore! And now you curse me because I've come home!?|Theon to [[Balon Greyjoy]]|What is Dead May Never Die}}
{{Quote|Gods help you Theon Greyjoy. Now you are truly lost.|[[Rodrik Cassel]]'s last words to Theon before his execution|The Old Gods and the New}}
{{Quote|I will kill that man! I swear it on the Drowned God, the Old Gods, the New Gods, and every fucking God in every fucking Heaven, I will kill that man!|Theon about [[Ramsay Snow]]|Valar Morghulis}}
{{Quote|Reek......my name.....is Reek.|'''Theon Greyjoy''' to Ramsay Snow|Mhysa}}
{{Quote|I'm Reek.......always......forever.|Theon Greyjoy/Reek|The Mountain and the Viper}}

